Package: hsrtools
Type: Package
Title: A Collection of Functions for Health Services research
Version: 0.0.1.9001
Authors@R: c(
    person("Catherine", "Blatter", email = "catherine.blatter@unibas.ch", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: hsrtools is a collection of functions written for questionnaire-studies in health services research.
    They cover elements for creating easily-usable graphs for sharing with the survey-participants. 
